This is an intraday long only strategy for options scalping. The key entry criteria are EMA 5 crossover EMA 13 provided the price is above or equal to VWAP AND EMA 21 ( trend filter for short term) . Also RSI si rising and at least 46. Exit is on stock closing below the low of the candle before the entry candle.
